title: Faceoff Hockey 2016 - SoN
description:
Game: Faceoff Hockey 2016
Coded: March 4, 2016 by SoN
Type: Installer

Description: Take over as coach and general manager of your favorite hockey franchise in this single season replay simulation. Make the choices to see if you could have turned out things differently in this game which features incredibly accurate stats and realistic strategic options. Play against the computer or join one of the long running FaceOff multiplayer online leagues for a new level of challenge.

Instructions: This is a full pre-cracked installer for the game. Install it and enjoy! It is as easy as that.

Notes: "Because the world is so full of death and horror, I try again and again to console my heart and pick the flowers that grow in the midst of hell." - Hermann Hesse
